# ============================================================================
# KEEP IN BUILD CONTEXT (Important files to include)
# ============================================================================
# The following files ARE included in the build:
# - auth/*.py (all Python source files)
# - auth/api/*.py (API route handlers)
# - auth/middleware/*.py (middleware components)
# - auth/models/*.py (data models)
# - auth/utils/*.py (utility functions)
# - requirements.txt (Python dependencies)
# - config.py (configuration)
#
# ============================================================================
# Build Optimization Notes:
# ============================================================================
# This .dockerignore file is designed to:
# 1. Reduce Docker build context size
# 2. Speed up image builds
# 3. Prevent sensitive data from being included
# 4. Exclude unnecessary development files
# 5. Maintain security best practices
#
# The distroless image will only contain:
# - Python runtime
# - Required Python packages
# - Application source code
# - Minimal dependencies for service operation
#
# ============================================================================

